"開啟行號
set nu
 
"不把太長的句子折下來
"set nowrap


"自動對齊
set ai


"使用c風格的自動縮進
set cindent

"語法高亮
syntax enable
syntax on



"光標那列特別標記
set cursorline
"光標那列標記設定
hi CursorLine cterm = bold ctermbg = DarkGrey ctermfg = none


"光標那行特別標記
set cursorcolumn
"光標那行標記設定
hi CursorColumn cterm = bold ctermbg = DarkGrey ctermfg = none

"輸入時自動搜尋
set incsearch

"將搜尋到的所有結果高亮
set hlsearch

